description:
It has been two seasons since we have seen Adrianna Nicole. Back then she was “Seven”. Adrianna is back and she’s serious about wanting to wrestle. She is big and strong, but she lacks technique.

Devi Lynne (ranked 7th) is Spartica! She’s a little 5’1 100 lb hellcat that is 100% go. This former college wrestler has great skill but is often out-gunned in size and weight. Can her experience be enough to overcome the 6 inches and 40lbs that her opponent has over her?
title: Devi Lynne "Spartica" (0-1) vs Adrianna Nicole "The Adrianaconda" (1-0)
